X-WR-CALNAME:Weaver line disruption
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-07-15T03:13:30&endDate=2026-07-16T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWeaver Line: Until Thursday 16th July\, there will be no service between Walthamstow Central and Chingford while we conduct urgent repairs to the track following a line side fire near Wood Street. Please use London Underground and London Buses to complete your journey. SEVERE DELAYS on the rest of the line. 
DTEND:20260716T002900Z
DTSTART:20260715T031330Z
SUMMARY:Weaver line: Severe Delays
UID:d134357b-f5b9-4b04-9ae3-9667cb1c869c@d134.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-07-19T03:30:00&endDate=2026-07-19T09:15:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWEAVER LINE: Sunday 19 July\, until 1015\, no service between Liverpool Street and Cheshunt / Chingford / Enfield Town. Use London Underground or London Buses via any reasonable route. GREATER ANGLIA trains will not call at Hackney Downs.\r\n\r\nRail replacement buses will run as follows: Service L1: Seven Sisters - Bruce Grove - White Hart Lane - Silver Street - Edmonton Green - Bush Hill Park - Enfield Town\; Service L2: Seven Sisters - Bruce Grove - White Hart Lane - Silver Street - Edmonton Green - Bush Hill Park - Southbury - Turkey Street - Theobalds Grove - Cheshunt\; Service L3: Hackney Downs - Clapton - St. James Street - Walthamstow Central - Wood Street - Highams Park - Chingford. \r\n\r\nFirst trains: Enfield Town to Liverpool Street 09:57\; Liverpool Street to Enfield Town 10:20\; First Liverpool Street to Cheshunt 10:12\; Cheshunt to Liverpool Street 10:01\; Liverpool Street to Chingford 10:02\; Chingford to Liverpool Street 10:08
DTEND:20260719T091500Z
DTSTART:20260719T033000Z
SUMMARY:Weaver line: Planned Closure
UID:087fe56a-86c5-498d-b5ca-9cc0383571cf@087f.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-07-23T21:45:00&endDate=2026-07-24T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWEAVER LINE: Monday 20\, Tuesday 21\, Wednesday 22 and Thursday 23 July\, after 2245 each evening\, no service between Hackney Downs and Enfield Town / Cheshunt. Last through trains operate at 2213 from Liverpool Street to Cheshunt\, 2250 from Enfield Town to Liverpool Street\, 2258 from Liverpool Street to Enfield Town and 2259 from Cheshunt to Liverpool Street. Use Clapton for Rectory Road and Stoke Newington\, and local London Buses services for Stamford Hill. Replacement buses operate. The limited number of southbound GREATER ANGLIA and STANSTED EXPRESS trains after midnight which usually call at Seven Sisters are diverted via Tottenham Hale instead
DTEND:20260724T002900Z
DTSTART:20260723T214500Z
SUMMARY:Weaver line: Part Closure
UID:0884dcb0-8cc1-43e9-bf0c-0d09e8367f71@0884.org
END:VEVENT
